r521 | carter | 2005-04-17 03:30:31 -0700 (Sun, 17 Apr 2005) | 5 lines

Fixed the Lifetime of Stk singleton instances.
This allows for a clean shutdown of all objects, especially backend objects at program exit(application object destroyal) time.

Introduces incompatible API change: Event producers must be created after the application object!

------------------------------------------------------------------------
