*** empty log message ***

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r506 | dvhart | 2004-10-23 10:12:38 -0700 (Sat, 23 Oct 2004) | 5 lines

Fixed the problem where you couldn't tab out of a list once you were in it.
list_item is no longer a focusable widget (the list is, and it handles all
events).  Widgets no longer "handle" (un)focus events if they aren't
focusable, they pass them up to the parent instead.  Finally!

------------------------------------------------------------------------
