r499 | dvhart | 2004-04-28 08:59:36 -0700 (Wed, 28 Apr 2004) | 2 lines

updated changelog

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r498 | dvhart | 2004-04-28 08:58:55 -0700 (Wed, 28 Apr 2004) | 8 lines

added font_props call to label and removed text_size
some cleanup, comments, and reordering in application.cpp
fixed widget navigation by having container return a null ptr when reaching the end or beginning of
 the children when focus_next|prev is called.  Added focus_next|prev to state that loops rather
  than returning null.  Also fixed container::focused() to be const, which is why it was never
   getting called.  Now we don't get trapped inside a container   like scroll_panel (test_app) with
    no way to navigate out with the keyboard.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
