r408 | dvhart | 2003-10-29 15:20:14 -0800 (Wed, 29 Oct 2003) | 2 lines

fixed text_area resizing bug by fixing the logical_or combiner.  It only executed some of the slots, it makes more since to execute all slots and then compare the results (this is different from the conditional of an if or a while), also updated logical_and for the same behavior.

