r365 | dvhart | 2003-10-07 15:33:45 -0700 (Tue, 07 Oct 2003) | 2 lines

surface_sdl::create now accepts a fullscreen parameter (defaulting to true), this is because surface_sdl is meant as a development surface and it may be desireable to develop the application in windowed mode, while deployed apps will invariably run fullscreen.  Hello_World uses windowed mode with SDL now, the other test apps all run fullscreen

