r336 | dvhart | 2003-09-17 13:10:38 -0700 (Wed, 17 Sep 2003) | 2 lines

fixed segfaults do to sdl_data using a shared_ptr to store instance_ instead of a weak_ptr, alleviated some density do to Marc's peculiar aversion to whitespace :-), and made drawable derive publicly from rectangle.  The last may not be ideal but since both widget and list_item need it, I started at drawable, It seems natural enough for a drawable to be a rect, except that application derives from it.... which it shouldn't anyway.

