r202 | dvhart | 2003-06-10 09:07:59 -0700 (Tue, 10 Jun 2003) | 2 lines

event_producer header

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r201 | dvhart | 2003-06-09 20:22:41 -0700 (Mon, 09 Jun 2003) | 15 lines

Primary Purpose: implement new event system model with one singleton event
  system and an arbitrary number of producers, employing either/both push
	and pull event production.
moved event constructor to protected
add operator()! to event
add event_producer abstract base class
made event_system non-abstract and a singleton
modified event_system to handle event_producers from various backends
converted event_system_sdl to event_producer_sdl
  event producers' create() method should call
event_system::get()->add_producer(new_producer)
updated application to use the singleton event_system
updated test applications to use new event system model
TODO: add scoped_lock() to the event_system around the events_ queue operations

------------------------------------------------------------------------
